metadata.name: Sacred Feminine
metadata.description:
Mermaids embody the sacred feminine, known as the goddess's of the sea they also symbolize awareness , good luck , happiness ahead and fertility in the ocean.
Many others know her as the destructive nature of the water with the ability to lure sailors to their deaths.

This piece is meaningful as it represents bravery, beauty, power, magic and a connection to nature..
She will teach you to find balance between your heart and mind to be as strong as the ocean tidal waves and as breathtaking as a mermaid.

Hand drawn digital painting in Procreate
3000x4800
